    "wizard_close_btn": "Rufe setup mai jagora. naka ci gaba shi ne ajiye da kai zai iya resume later.",
    "wizard_complete_btn": "Kammala mai jagora da samar da naka darasi tare da duka configured saiti applied.",
    "wizard_content_next_btn": "Proceed zuwa na gaba abun ciki creation mataki mai jagora.",
    "wizard_find_standard_btn": "Bincika don educational mizani wancan match naka abun ciki topic.",
    "wizard_grade_option": "Zaɓi wannan matakin aji don naka darasi. Determines ƙamus da concept rikitarwa.",
    "wizard_growth_goal_input": "Shigar koyo growth manufa don ɗalibi zuwa achieve tare da wannan abun ciki.",
