    "persona_select_button": "Zaɓi wannan persona zuwa begin naka interview ko conversation. Once zaɓ, kai'll shigar mai zurfafawa tattaunawa interface ina kai zai iya ask tambaya, bincika their perspective, da earn XP don meaningful exchanges. AI responds bisa kan tafarki's historical knowledge, personality, da cultural context.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return zuwa persona selection screen zuwa zaɓi different tafarki. naka current conversation ci gaba shi ne automatically ajiye, da kai zai iya return zuwa ci gaba it later. wannan allows exploring da yawa perspectives kan same historical topic.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Ƙara na musamman requirements don yaya persona should behave during conversations. misali: focus kan na musamman time period, emphasize certain beliefs ko darajar, maintain particular speech patterns, ko limit responses zuwa historically accurate knowledge. malami zai iya yi amfani wannan zuwa align personas tare da na musamman koyo objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Zaɓi yaya persona responds zuwa ƙirƙira different koyo gogewa. IN tafarki: Fully mai zurfafawa historical murya tare da no yanayirn explanations. EDUCATIONAL: tafarki speaks amma ya haɗ da koyo scaffolds, ƙamus tallafi, da context. MIXED: Balanced approach tare da authentic murya plus occasional clarifications. Zaɓi bisa kan ɗalibi readiness da koyo manufa.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type naka own buɗe-ended response instead na selecting daga pre-written zaɓi. Free response yanayi promotes creative expression, critical thinking, da authentic dialogue fasaha. Responses su ne analyzed don historical accuracy, empathy, da zurfi na inquiry. Higher-quality tambaya earn ƙari XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Nuna ko ɓoye response suggestions da conversation shawara. lokacin enabled, tsarin provides scaffolded tambaya starters, historical conrubutu prompts, da engagement suggestions. Taimakoful don ɗalibi sabon zuwa historical inquiry ko those needing tallafi tare da buɗe-ended tambayaing. malami zai iya kashe shawara don ƙari na ci-gaba tantance scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Display taimakoful shawara don mai jan hankali tare da persona. shawara haɗ historically relevant tambaya zuwa ask, topics tafarki would find interesting, da prompts wancan lead zuwa deeper understanding. Great don ɗalibi who need scaffolding ko aren't sure yaya zuwa begin historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Aika naka saƙo zuwa persona tafarki. naka tambaya ko response shi ne analyzed don relevance da zurfi. AI persona za respond authentically bisa kan their historical context, knowledge, da personality. Well-crafted tambaya wancan nuna historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
    "persona_close": "Rufe panel ɗin tattaunawa na persona. Tarihin tattaunawarka da XP da ka samu ana ajiye su kai-tsaye. Kana iya ci gaba da wannan tattaunawa daga baya daga shafin Tarihi.",
    "persona_close_title": "Rufe Persona tattaunawa",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Rubuta tunaninka kan tattaunawar don tantancewa. Yi tunani kan abin da ka koya game da mutumin tarihi, yadda mahangarsa ta bambanta da ra'ayoyin zamani, da yadda wannan tattaunawa ta canza fahimtarka. Ana tantance tunani ta amfani da ma'auni (rubric) da ya jitu da ƙwarewar tunani na tarihi kuma yana iya samun XP mai yawa.",
    "persona_conclude": "End conversation da samar da comprehensive summary na naka discussion. summary ya haɗ da: key topics covered, historical insights gained, quality na naka tambaya, empathy demonstrated, da XP earned. wannan summary zai iya be exported don tantance, added zuwa ɗalibi portfolios, ko yi amfani as writing prompt don tunani activities.",
    "persona_save_chat": "Ajiye wannan conversation zuwa bita ko raba later. Adanad chats preserve kammala dialogue, XP earned, timestamps, da any tunanis. Yi amfani ajiye chats don ɗalibi portfolios, tantance evidence, aji discussions, ko exemplar yanayils. Adanad conversations zai iya be exported as PDF ko shared tare da other ɗalibi.",
    "persona_topic_spark": "Get conversation starter ko topic suggestion lokacin kai're ba sure menene zuwa ask. tsarin na samarwa historically relevant tambaya bisa kan persona's background, expertise, da time period. Great don overcoming writer's block ko discovering sabon kusurwa zuwa bincika naka historical inquiry.",
    "persona_auto_send": "Automatically aika naka saƙo lokacin kai tsayar typing don few seconds. Creates ƙari natural conversational flow, especially lokacin amfani murya dictation. Kashe wannan idan kai prefer zuwa bita da gyara saƙo before sending, ko idan kai need ƙari time zuwa compose thoughtful responses.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Yi nazari naka tushe rubutu don reading matakin, rikitarwa, da fasaloli.",
    "analysis_check_accuracy": "Fact-check tushe abun ciki against reliable references.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Samar da gani organizer daga naka tushe abun ciki.",
    "timeline_generate_button": "Samar da timeline na events daga naka tushe abun ciki.",
    "timeline_topic": "main topic ko jigon na timeline being samar. AI ƙirƙira historically accurate events bisa kan wannan topic da naka tushe abun ciki. misali topics: American Revolution, Life Cycle na Stars, Shakespeare's Career. Events su ne automatically ordered chronologically don sequencing horo.",
    "timeline_count": "lamba na events zuwa haɗ timeline. ƙari events ƙirƙira longer, ƙari cikakke timelines amma increase wahala. Recommended: 4-6 events don beginners, 8-10 don na tsakiya, 12+ don na ci-gaba learners. Events su ne draggable don sequencing horo after generation.",
    "faq_custom_instructions": "Ƙara na musamman requirements don FAQ tambaya (e.g., 'Focus kan misconceptions').",
    "faq_count": "lamba na FAQ tambaya-amsa pairs zuwa samar da.",
    "lesson_plan_custom_additions": "Ƙara na musamman activities, mizani, ko abun ciki zuwa haɗ darasi plan.",
    "group_modal_container": "aji rukuni manager don organizing ɗalibi da albarkatu.",
    "group_create_input": "Shigar name don sabon ɗalibi rukuni.",
    "group_create_button": "Ƙirƙira sabon ɗalibi rukuni tare da entered name.",
    "group_roster_list": "List na ɗalibi zaɓ rukuni.",
    "roster_panel_header": "aji Roster Key shi ne naka differentiation command center. Ƙirƙira ɗalibi rukunis tare da unique koyo profiles (matakin aji, harshe, reading matakin, interests, DOK), then apply those profiles zuwa any generator. Roster bayanai shi ne stored naka browser's local storage da never leaves naka device unless kai explicitly fitar ko sync zuwa kai-tsaye zama. Yi amfani 'Aiwatar zuwa Generator' zuwa instantly configure saiti don rukuni, ko 'Differentiate by Group' zuwa batch-samar da albarkatu don duka rukunis at once.",
    "roster_import_export": "Shigo previously exported roster JSON fayil, ko fitar naka current roster don backup ko sharing between devices. Exported fayil contain rukuni names, launi, ɗalibi assignments, da duka profile saiti.",
    "roster_sync_session": "Push naka roster rukuni metadata zuwa mai aiki Firebase zama so ɗalibi su ne automatically assigned zuwa their designated rukuni lokacin they join. Group-na musamman saiti (TTS gudu, karaoke yanayi) take effect kan ɗalibi devices.",
    "roster_batch_generate": "Samar da albarkatu daban-daban ga kowace ƙungiya a lokaci guda. Zaɓi waɗanne nau'ikan albarkatu za a ƙirƙira (rubutu da aka daidaita, ƙamus, gwaji, da sauransu) kuma tsarin zai bi ta kowace ƙungiya, yana amfani da saitin bayanan martabarsu kafin samarwa. Ana yiwa albarkatun lakabi da alamomin ƙungiya don sauƙin tacewa.",
    "bridge_send_button": "Buɗe Bridge yanayi zuwa aika harsuna biyu saƙo zuwa ɗalibi during kai-tsaye umarni. Type concept, jimla, ko umarni, zaɓi yanayi (Explain, Translate, ko gani+Explain), da zaɓi target rukuni. saƙo shi ne samar amfani AI tare da rukuni's harshe da reading matakin saiti, then displayed as large, readable harsuna biyu panel kan ɗalibi devices tare da TTS da karaoke highlighting.",
    "group_active_list": "Currently mai aiki ɗalibi rukunis tare da assigned albarkatu.",
