      "per_grade_skills_checklists_use_during": "Jerin dubawa na ƙwarewa ga kowane aji. Yi amfani a lokacin tantancewar mutum-ɗaya ko don tsara koyarwa.",
      "my_child_says_i_hate_fractions": "Ɗana yana cewa «Ina ƙin kaso»",
      "very_common_fractions_break_the_rules_": "Gama gari sosai. Kaso suna karya ƙa'idodin da ɗalibai suke koyo don lambobi cika — manyan lambobi ba koyaushe suke nufin manyan darajoji ba. Takaici na gaskiya ne kuma na yau da kullum. Taimaka ta: (1) yin amfani da samfuran gani kamar pizza ko zaren kaso, (2) haɗawa da rayuwa ta gaskiya (girki, lokaci, kuɗi), (3) yin aiki kaɗan-kaɗan akai-akai (mintuna 5 a rana) maimakon dogon zama, (4) yaba ƙoƙari, ba amsoshi daidai kaɗai ba.",
      "my_child_doesn_t_understand_why_proced": "Ɗana bai fahimci DALILIN da yasa hanyoyi suke aiki ba",
      "they_are_not_alone_most_students_learn": "Ba su kaɗai ba — yawancin ɗalibai suna koyon hanya da farko sannan dalili daga baya. Taimaka ta hanyar nuna koyaushe yadda hanyar take kama da hoto. «Ninka 3/4 da 1/2» za a iya zana shi a matsayin murabba'i mai kusurwa huɗu. Shafin Op Proofs yana yin wannan a gare ka. Tambaya «me yasa?» a hankali kuma akai-akai.",
      "how_can_i_help_with_homework_without_d": "Ta yaya zan taimaka da aikin gida ba tare da yi masa ba?",
      "use_the_worked_examples_tab_they_show_": "Yi amfani da shafin Worked Examples — suna nuna hanyoyi mataki-mataki tare da tunani. Yi matsaloli masu kama tare, ba iri ɗaya ba. Idan sun ce «Ban san yadda zan fara ba,» tambaya «Menene matsalar take neman ka samu? Me muka riga muka sani?» Tsarin alamu a Word Problems yana ba da alamu masu layi-layi — gwada na farko kafin amsar.",
      "what_should_i_drill": "Menene zan yi aikin sa?",
      "ies_practice_guide_recommends_1_magnit": "IES Practice Guide tana ba da shawara: (1) tunani na girma (aikin layin lamba), (2) haɗi tsakanin gani da alama, (3) matsalolin kalmomi a mahalli. GUJI: aiki kan hanyoyi ba tare da fahimta ba. Ciyar da mintuna 5 kan Benchmark Trainer, 5 kan Word Problems, da 5 kan wasa — wannan zama mai kyau ne na mintuna 15.",
      "my_child_gets_the_procedure_right_but_": "Ɗana yana samun hanyar daidai amma amsar ba daidai ba",
      "usually_means_a_small_arithmetic_error": "Yawanci yana nufin ƙaramin kuskuren lissafi (misali, ya ninka ba daidai ba) ko bai sauƙaƙa ba. Nuna masu Cheat Sheet — za su iya duba aikinsu mataki-mataki. Ƙarfafa su su tabbatar da wata hanya (kimanta da farko, ko yi amfani da samfuri daban).",
      "what_if_i_don_t_remember_fractions_wel": "Idan ni kaina ban tuna kaso da kyau fa?",
      "you_don_t_have_to_be_the_expert_use_th": "Ba dole ne ka zama gwani ba! Yi amfani da Tab Guide da Worked Examples — suna bayyana hanyoyi a fili. Mafi kyau: nuna misalin «bari mu gano wannan tare.» Za ka iya koyo tare da ɗanka. Shafin Vocabulary yana da amfani har ga manya.",
      "how_do_i_know_if_my_child_is_on_track": "Ta yaya zan san ko ɗana yana kan hanya madaidaiciya?",
      "look_at_the_standards_tab_to_see_which": "Duba shafin Standards don ganin waɗanne ka'idojin CCSS ya kamata su sani don ajinsu. Shafin Mastery yana nuna ci gaba. Don dubawa mai sauri: shin za su iya (a) zana samfuri don 3/4, (b) faɗi kaso daidai da 1/2, (c) kwatanta 2/3 da 3/4 kuma su bayyana? Waɗannan gwaje-gwaje uku sun rufe yawancin tsammanin kaso na K-5.",
      "parent_guide": "👨‍👩‍👧 Jagorar iyaye",
      "guidance_for_parents_helping_kids_with": "Jagora ga iyaye masu taimaka wa yara da kaso a gida. Ƙalubale na gama gari, shawarwari masu amfani, da abin da za a tambaya.",
