      "let_your_number_be_n_the_sequence_n_1_": "Bari lambarka ta zama n. Jerin: (n+1) × 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n + 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n. Raba da 2 → n. Cire na asali → 0. Jira — wannan yana ba da 0, ba 1 ba. Gwada: n → (n+1)×2 = 2n+2 → +4 = 2n+6 → −6 = 2n → ÷2 = n → −na asali = 0. «Dabarar» tana dogara ne kan lambobi ɓoyayyu a jeri.",
