      "each_term_is_half_the_previous_the_tot": "Kowace istilahi rabin da ta gabata ce. Jimla tana kusanci 1 amma ba ta kai gaba ɗaya. Wannan jeri ne na geometric mara iyaka mai istilahin farko 1/2 da rabo 1/2: S = (1/2) / (1 − 1/2) = 1. Shi ya sa sabanin motsi na Zeno za a iya warware shi a lissafance.",
      "the_harmonic_series": "Jerin harmonic (harmonic series)",
      "even_though_each_term_is_small_the_ser": "Ko da yake kowace istilahi ƙarama ce, jerin yana watsewa. Don wuce 100, kana buƙatar kimanin istilahi 1.5 × 10^43. An tabbatar da wannan da Nicole Oresme a shekarun 1300 ta amfani da ƙungiyoyi: 1/3 + 1/4 > 1/4 + 1/4 = 1/2; 1/5+...+1/8 > 4 × 1/8 = 1/2; koyaushe za ka iya samun wani 1/2 na ƙarawa.",
      "farey_sequences": "Jerin Farey",
      "check_1_4_and_1_3_4_1_1_3_1_check_2_5_": "Duba 1/4 da 1/3: (4)(1) − (1)(3) = 1. Duba 2/5 da 1/2: (5)(1) − (2)(2) = 1. Wannan kadara tana samar da itacen Stern-Brocot na dukkan lambobin hankali.",
      "multiplying_telescopes": "Na'urorin hangen nesa masu ninkawa (telescopes)",
