      "read_v_formation_explanation_aloud": "Karanta bayanin tsarin V da babbar murya",
      "read_aloud": "🔊 Karanta da Babbar Murya",
      "v_formation_simulator_canvas_drag_bird": "Allon kwaikwayon tsarin V. Ja tsuntsaye don canza matsayinsu. An yiwa tsuntsun da ke jagoranci alama da tauraro. Sandunan kuzari a saman kowane tsuntsu suna nuna matakin kuzarinsa na yanzu. Kwanukan kore a bayan kowane tsuntsu suna nuna yankunan hawan-iska, inda tsuntsayen baya ke adana kuzari. Yankin ja kai tsaye a baya yana nuna yankin saukar-iska.",
