      "how_v_formation_works": "🪿 Yadda Tsarin V ke Aiki",
      "when_a_bird_flaps_its_wings_it_creates": "Sa'ad da tsuntsu ya buga fikafikansa, yana haifar da guguwar iska mai juyawa a kan kowane ƙarshen fiffike. Iskar da ke kai tsaye a baya da ƙasan ƙarshen fiffike ana turata ƙasa ",
      "downwash_but_the_air_to_the_side_pushe": " (saukar-iska), amma iskar da ke gefe ana turata sama ",
      "by_positioning_themselves_in_the_upwas": "Ta hanyar sanya kansu a yankin hawan-iska — kimanin 30° a baya da gefen tsuntsun da ke gaba — tsuntsayen baya suna samun tallafi kyauta daga iskar da ke tashi. A cikin garke na gaske wannan yana adana kimanin ",
      "of_their_energy": " na kuzarinsu (",
      "is_a_theoretical_maximum": " shine iyakar ka'ida).",
      "the_leader_gets_no_benefit_and_tires_f": "Jagora ba ya samun wata fa'ida kuma yana gajiya da sauri. Sa'ad da kuzarinsa ya faɗi ƙasa da 30%, yana koma baya kuma wani tsuntsu ya ɗauki jagoranci. Ana kiran wannan ",
      "leader_rotation": "juyawar jagoranci",
      "in_nature_every_bird_takes_a_turn_at_t": ". A cikin yanayi kowane tsuntsu yana ɗaukar lokacinsa a gaba.",
      "try_dragging_birds_into_different_posi": "Gwada jan tsuntsaye zuwa matsayai daban-daban don ganin yadda ƙwarewar tsari da adana kuzari ke canzawa! Danna V don ƙirƙira ta atomatik, S don warwatsa.",
      "formation_science": "🔬 Ilimin Tsari",
      "migration_world_records": "🏆 Rikodin Duniya na Ƙaura",
      "energy_budget_calculator": "⚡ Na'urar Lissafin Kasafin Kuzari",
      "adjust_the_sliders_to_see_how_distance": "Daidaita masu zamewa don ganin yadda nisa, girman jiki, iska da tsari ke shafar buƙatun kuzarin tsuntsu. Wannan yana kwaikwayon ainihin kimiyyar lissafi na tashin ƙaura.",
      "kcal_needed": "kcal da ake Buƙata",
      "fat_required": "Kitse da ake Buƙata",
      "of_body_weight": "na nauyin jiki",
      "insects_equivalent": "Daidai da Ƙwari",
      "the_science": "Kimiyya: ",
      "bird_flight_costs_12x_their_resting_me": "Tashin tsuntsu yana kashe kimanin sau 12 na yawan metabolism ɗinsa na hutawa (dokar Kleiber). Kitse yana ba da 9 kcal a kowace gram — mai da yake da mafi girman kuzari a ilimin halittu. Kafin ƙaura tsuntsaye suna shiga cikin ",
      "a_feeding_frenzy_where_they_may_double": " — hauka na ci, inda za su iya ninka nauyin jikinsu da kitse. Bar-tailed Godwit yana ƙona ",
      "55_of_its_body_weight": "55% na nauyin jikinsa",
      "during_its_7_145_mile_non_stop_flight_": " a lokacin tashinsa na mil 7,145 ba tare da tsayawa ba daga Alaska zuwa New Zealand.",
      "this_journey_requires_more_fat_than_th": "⚠️ Wannan tafiya tana buƙatar kitse fiye da nauyin tsuntsu! Zai buƙaci wuraren cika mai — ko tsarin V don rage kashe kuɗi.",
      "altitude_physiology": "✈️ Ilimin Halittar Tsawo",
      "some_birds_migrate_at_extreme_altitude": "Wasu tsuntsaye suna ƙaura a tsanani na tsawo — Bar-headed Geese suna ƙetare Himalaya a ƙafa 29,000. Ja mai zamewa don ganin yadda yanayi ke canzawa.",
      "air_density": "Ƙarfin Iska",
      "wind": "Iska",
      "extreme_altitude": "Tsanani na tsawo! ",
      "bar_headed_geese_survive_here_thanks_t": "Bar-headed Geese suna rayuwa a nan saboda hemoglobin da ke ɗaure oxygen da ƙarfi, huhu masu girma da mitochondria masu inganci. Yawancin dabbobi masu shayarwa za su suma a wannan tsawo. Jininsu yana da wani sauyi na musamman na hemoglobin (Pro→Ala a matsayi na 119) da ke ƙara jan hankalin oxygen da 50%.",
      "high_altitude_zone": "Yankin tsawo mai girma. ",
      "many_songbirds_migrate_at_this_range_w": "Yawancin tsuntsayen waƙa suna ƙaura a wannan matsayi, inda iska mai sirara ke rage jawo amma oxygen kaɗan ne. Tsuntsaye suna ramawa wannan da numfashi mai inganci: tsarin gudanar iska na hanya ɗaya yana fitar da oxygen a lokacin shaƙa da fitar da numfashi, sabanin huhun dabbobi masu shayarwa da ke fitar da shi a lokacin shaƙa kaɗai.",
      "common_cruising_altitude": "Tsawon tafiya na yau da kullum. ",
      "most_migrants_fly_between_5_000_15_000": "Yawancin masu ƙaura suna tashi tsakanin ƙafa 5,000 da 15,000. Zafin iska yana faɗuwa kimanin 3.5 °F a kowace ƙafa 1,000 (matsayin gradient na zafi). Tsuntsaye suna zaɓar tsawo don samun iska mai kyau — tsuntsu ɗaya zai iya tashi ƙafa 2,000 dare ɗaya da ƙafa 12,000 dare na gaba.",
      "low_altitude": "Ƙarancin tsawo. ",
      "hummingbirds_and_some_shorebirds_fly_c": "Hummingbirds da wasu tsuntsayen bakin teku suna tashi kusa da saman, musamman a kan ruwa. Tashi ƙasa yana da aminci daga daskarewar ƙanƙara, amma yana nufin ƙarin turjiyar iska da ƙarancin tallafin iska. Yayin ƙetare Tekun Mexico na mil 600, yawancin tsuntsaye suna tashi tsakanin ƙafa 1,000 da 3,000.",
      "mountain": "Dutse",
      "deflects_wind_upward_on_windward_side": "yana karkatar da iska sama a gefen da ke fuskantar iska",
      "building": "Gini",
      "creates_turbulent_wake": "yana haifar da hayaƙin damuwa",
      "lake": "Tafki",
      "sea_breeze_thermal_effect": "tasirin zafi na iskar teku",
      "thermal": "Magudanar Zafi",
