      "forest": "Daji",
      "friction_slows_wind_near_surface": "gogayya yana rage saurin iska kusa da saman",
      "add_a_bird_to_ride_the_wind_currents": "Ƙara tsuntsu don hawa magudanan iska",
      "add_bird": "🐦 Ƙara Tsuntsu",
      "clear_all_objects_and_birds": "Share dukkan abubuwa da tsuntsaye",
      "clear_all": "🗑️ Share Duka",
      "wind_direction": "Alkiblar Iska",
      "wind_2": "🌬️ Iska:",
      "wind_science_for_migrators": "🌬️ Ilimin Iska ga Masu Ƙaura",
      "thermals": "Magudanan Zafi",
      "thermals_are_columns_of_rising_warm_ai": "Magudanan zafi ginshiƙai ne na iska mai ɗumi da ke tashi da ake haifar sa'ad da rana ta ɗumama ƙasa ba daidai ba. Saman duhu (wuraren ajiye motoci, gonaki da aka nome) suna haifar da magudanai masu ƙarfi fiye da saman haske (ruwa, daji). Tsuntsaye masu shawagi kamar shaho da gaggafa suna hawa cikin lanƙwasa a magudanan zafi, suna samun tsawo ba tare da buga fikafikai ba. Sannan suna zamewa zuwa magudana ta gaba, suna haifar da “babbar hanyar zafi”, hanya mai sauri mai inganci a sararin sama.",
      "orographic_lift": "Ɗagawar Duwatsu",
      "when_wind_encounters_a_mountain_it_is_": "Sa'ad da iska ta gamu da dutse, ana turata sama a gefen gangaren da ke fuskantar iska. Wannan yana haifar da igiyar iska mai tashi da tsuntsaye masu shawagi (kamar gaggafa masu zinariya) ke amfani da su a kan kololuwa. A gefen da ba ya fuskantar iska, iska tana nutsewa da sauri, tana haifar da yanki mai haɗari na “rotor” na iska mai damuwa da ke saukowa. Shi ya sa tsuntsaye da matukan jirgi ke guje wa gefen da ba ya fuskantar iska na duwatsu.",
      "sea_breezes": "Iskar Teku",
      "land_heats_faster_than_water_during_th": "Ƙasa tana ɗumama da sauri fiye da ruwa da rana. Iska mai ɗumi tana tashi a kan ƙasa kuma iska mai sanyi tana zuwa daga teku don ɗaukar matsayinta, tana haifar da “iskar teku” zuwa gaɓar teku. Da dare tsarin yana juyawa. Tsuntsaye masu ƙaura suna amfani da waɗannan iskar gaɓar da ake iya hasashe don adana kuzari. Yankin haɗuwa, inda iskar teku ke haɗuwa da iskar ciki, sau da yawa yana haifar da magudanan zafi da tsuntsaye ke amfani da su don samun tsawo.",
      "jet_streams": "Magudanan Jet",
      "high_altitude_jet_streams_are_narrow_b": "Magudanan jet na tsawo mai girma ƙunƙunta ne na iska mai sauri sosai (100-200 mph) a ƙafa 30,000-40,000. Ko da yake yawancin tsuntsaye suna tashi ƙasa da magudanan jet, wasu masu ƙaura kamar Bar-tailed Godwit suna hawa sama da ƙafa 20,000 don kama iska mai kyau ta tsawo mai girma. An gano tumaki (geese) ta radar a ƙafa 29,000 a kan Himalaya, inda oxygen kaɗan ne kuma zafi yana faɗuwa zuwa -50 °F.",
      "wind_shear": "Yankewar Iska",
      "wind_shear_is_a_sudden_change_in_wind_": "Yankewar iska canji ne kwatsam a saurin iska ko alkibla a cikin ɗan nisa. Yana da haɗari ga tsuntsaye da jiragen sama. A lokacin hadari, ƙananan fashewa (ginshiƙan iska kwatsam da ke saukowa) suna haifar da yankewar iska mai tsanani kusa da ƙasa. Tsuntsaye suna jin canje-canjen matsi kuma sau da yawa suna jinkirta ƙaura sa'ad da fuskokin hadari ke gabatowa.",
      "beaufort_scale": "Ma'aunin Beaufort",
      "admiral_sir_francis_beaufort_created_h": "Admiral Sir Francis Beaufort ya ƙirƙira ma'aunin iskarsa a shekara ta 1805 dangane da tasirin iska a kan jiragen ruwa masu tuƙi. Ma'aunin Beaufort na zamani yana amfani da lura da ƙasa: ƙarfi 0 (kwanciyar hankali) = hayaƙi yana tashi tsaye; ƙarfi 6 (iska mai ƙarfi) = manyan rassa suna girgiza, laima suna juyewa; ƙarfi 12 (guguwa) = hallaka. Yawancin tsuntsaye sun fi son ƙaura a ƙarfi 2-4 (iska mai sauƙi zuwa matsakaici).",
      "how_birds_use_wind": "🐦 Yadda Tsuntsaye ke Amfani da Iska",
      "tail_winds": "Iskar Baya: ",
      "migrants_strongly_prefer_flying_with_t": "Masu ƙaura sun fi son tashi da iska a bayansu. Iskar baya ta 15 mph kaɗai tana ninka saurin tsuntsu dangane da ƙasa yadda ya kamata a kashe kuzari iri ɗaya. Nazarce-nazarce sun nuna motsin tsuntsaye ya ninka sau 10 a ranakun ƙaura masu iska mai kyau ta baya fiye da ranakun iskar gaba.",
      "dynamic_soaring": "Shawagi Mai Ƙarfi: ",
      "albatrosses_exploit_wind_speed_gradien": "Albatross suna amfani da gradient na saurin iska a kan raƙuman teku. Ta hanyar canjawa tsakanin hawa cikin iska mai sauri da nutsewa cikin iska mai jinkiri kusa da saman, suna fitar da kuzari daga yankewar iska da kanta. Albatross zai iya tashi mil dubbai kusan ba tare da buga fikafikai ba.",
      "slope_soaring": "Shawagin Gangare: ",
      "when_wind_hits_a_cliff_face_or_ridge_t": "Sa'ad da iska ta buga fuskar dutse ko kwazazzabo, iska da take dawowa tana haifar da “igiya” ta ɗagawa tare da layin kwazazzabo. Tsuntsaye masu farauta suna shawagi a kan waɗannan magudanan kwazazzabo a lokacin ƙaura, suna haɗa tsaunuka kamar tsalle a kan duwatsu. Hawk Mountain a Pennsylvania sananne ne saboda wannan lamari.",
      "experiment_place_a_thermal_and_a_mount": "Gwaji: Sanya magudanar zafi da dutse a filin, sannan ƙara tsuntsu. Kalli shi yana shawagi a kan magudanai masu tashi!",
      "birds_as_weather_forecasters": "🌦️ Tsuntsaye a Matsayin Masu Hasashen Yanayi",
      "birds_are_exquisitely_sensitive_to_wea": "Tsuntsaye suna da matuƙar hankali ga canje-canjen yanayi kuma an yi amfani da su a matsayin “barometer masu rai” a duk tarihi:",
      "barometric_pressure": "Matsin Barometer: ",
      "birds_can_detect_changes_in_barometric": "Tsuntsaye za su iya gano canje-canje a matsin barometer saboda masu karɓa na musamman a tsakiyar kunne (gaɓar paratympanic). Sa'ad da matsi ya faɗi kafin hadari, tsuntsaye sau da yawa suna tashi ƙasa kuma suna ci da ƙarfi. Alaru masu tashi ƙasa alama ce ta gargajiya ta hadari.",
      "some_birds_can_hear_infrasound_below_2": "Wasu tsuntsaye za su iya jin infrasound (ƙasa da 20 Hz) da ake samarwa ko da daga hadari masu nisa, raƙuman teku da girgizar ƙasa. Kamar yadda masu watsa GPS suka gano, Golden-winged Warblers sun bar Tennessee sa'o'i 24 kafin tsarin guguwa ya isa a 2014. Sun tashi fiye da mil 900 don guje wa hadari.",
      "cold_fronts": "Fuskokin Sanyi: ",
      "autumn_migration_is_strongly_correlate": "Ƙaura na kaka tana da alaƙa mai ƙarfi da wucewar fuskokin sanyi. Tsuntsaye suna shawagi a kan iskar arewa-maso-yamma a bayan fuskokin sanyi, waɗanda ke ba da iskar baya da sararin sama mai tsabta. Masu kallon tsuntsaye ƙwararru suna sa ido kan taswirorin yanayi don hasashen daren mafi girman ƙaura.",
      "fog_is_dangerous_for_migrating_birds_b": "Hazo yana da haɗari ga tsuntsaye masu ƙaura saboda yana ɓoye alamun ƙasa da alamun kewayawa na sararin sama. Daren hazo mai ƙarancin gizagizai yana haifar da “faɗuwa”, inda tsuntsaye masu ƙaura da suka gaji ke sauka a garke a mazauni na farko da ke akwai. Waɗannan abubuwan, ko da yake suna damun tsuntsaye, suna haifar da damar kallon tsuntsaye mai ban mamaki.",
      "when_the_swallows_fly_high_the_weather": "“Idan alaru suka tashi sama, yanayi zai bushe. Idan alaru suka tashi ƙasa, ruwan sama na kan hanya.” — Wannan karin maganar gargajiya a zahiri daidai ne a kimiyance: ƙwari (abincin alaru) suna tashi sama a tsarin matsi mai girma da ƙasa kafin hadari.",
      "particle_color_guide": "🎨 Jagoran Launin Ƙwaya",
