      "when_do_birds_migrate": "📅 Yaushe Tsuntsaye ke Ƙaura?",
      "migration_timing_varies_dramatically_b": "Lokacin ƙaura yana bambanta sosai bisa ga nau'i:",
      "early_spring_waterfowl_ducks_geese_hea": "Farkon bazara: Tsuntsayen ruwa (agwagi, tumaki) suna nufin arewa suna bin narkewar ƙanƙara. Red-winged Blackbirds suna komawa fadama.",
      "peak_spring_warblers_vireos_tanagers_f": "Mafi girman bazara: Warblers, vireos da tanagers suna cika arewa. Yawancin tsuntsayen waƙa suna ƙaura da dare. A daren mafi girma akwai tsuntsaye sama da miliyan 500 a sararin sama.",
      "shorebirds_start_south_some_species_fa": "Tsuntsayen bakin teku suna farawa kudu — wasu nau'ikan sun “gaza” a wuraren haihuwa kuma suna fara komawa da wuri a farkon Yuli. Manya sau da yawa suna tafiya kafin 'ya'ya.",
      "peak_fall_raptors_ride_thermals_along_": "Mafi girman kaka: Masu farauta suna hawa magudanan zafi tare da tsaunuka. Tsuntsayen waƙa suna nufin kudu suna bin fuskokin sanyi. Tumaki (geese) suna tashi cikin tsarin V da dare.",
      "photoperiod_day_length_is_the_primary_": "Tsawon rana shine babban abin da ke haddasa ƙaura. Yayin da ranaku ke gajarta a kaka, hormones suna haddasa “Zugunruhe” — rashin nutsuwa na ƙaura — kuma tsuntsaye suna fara tara ajiyar kitse (yawan ci), wani lokacin suna ninka nauyin jiki.",
      "stopover_ecology": "⛺ Ilimin Muhalli na Wuraren Tsayawa",
      "stopovers_are_not_just_rest_stops_they": "Wuraren tsayawa ba wuraren hutu kaɗai ba ne, su ",
      "refueling_stations": "tashoshin cika mai",
      "critical_to_survival_a_migrating_warbl": " ne masu muhimmanci ga rayuwa. Warbler mai ƙaura zai iya kashe 75% na lokacin ƙaura a wuraren tsayawa, yana ci da hauka don sake gina ajiyar kitse. Ingantaccen mazaunin wurin tsayawa zai iya zama bambanci tsakanin rayuwa da mutuwa.",
      "at_delaware_bay_over_1_million_shorebi": "A Delaware Bay, sama da tsuntsayen bakin teku miliyan 1 (Red Knots, Ruddy Turnstones, Sanderlings) sun dogara da ƙwan kaguwar doki da aka sa a Mayu. Lokaci dole ne ya yi daidai: tsuntsaye suna zuwa daidai lokacin da kaguwar doki ke sa ƙwai. Idan yawan kaguwar doki ya faɗi (saboda yawan kamun kifi don ƙugiya), duk sarƙar ƙaura ta ruguje.",
      "conservation_success_story_after_horse": "Labarin nasarar kiyayewa: Bayan an gabatar da iyakokin girbin kaguwar doki a 2012, yawan Red Knot ya fara farfaɗowa a hankali daga mafi ƙasƙanci na rikici na 15,000 zuwa sama da 50,000 nan da 2025.",
      "migration_physiology": "🦴 Ilimin Halittar Ƙaura",
      "migration_is_one_of_the_most_physicall": "Ƙaura ɗaya ce daga cikin ayyuka masu buƙatar ƙarfin jiki mafi girma a masarautar dabbobi. Tsuntsaye suna shiga sauye-sauye masu ban mamaki na jiki kafin tashi:",
      "hyperphagia": "Yawan Ci",
      "before_migration_birds_enter_a_feeding": "Kafin ƙaura, tsuntsaye suna shiga hauka na ci da ake kira yawan ci, suna ci a yawan sau 2-3 fiye da na yau da kullum. Blackpoll Warbler (gram 12) yana ƙara ajiyar kitse na gram 8-12, kusan yana ninka nauyin jiki. Wannan kitse shine mai don tashe-tashe ba tare da tsayawa ba na sama da mil 2,000.",
      "organ_shrinkage": "Ƙanƙantar Gaɓoɓi",
      "to_reduce_weight_migrating_birds_actua": "Don rage nauyi, tsuntsaye masu ƙaura suna ƙanƙantar da gaɓoɓin narkewa (hanji, hanta, tumbi) har zuwa 40% kafin tashi. Sa'ad da suka isa wuraren tsayawa, suna sake gina waɗannan gaɓoɓin da sauri don cika mai. Wannan “sassauƙan phenotype” na musamman ne a cikin dabbobi masu kashin baya.",
      "hemoglobin": "Hemoglobin",
      "high_altitude_migrants_like_bar_headed": "Masu ƙaura na tsawo mai girma kamar Bar-headed Geese (masu tashi ƙafa 29,000 a kan Himalaya) suna da hemoglobin na musamman mai jan hankalin oxygen fiye da haka. Tsokokinsu suna ɗauke da ƙarin myoglobin, kuma ƙarfin capillary ɗinsu ninki biyu ne na nau'ikan ƙasa.",
      "sleep_in_flight": "Barci Yayin Tashi",
      "some_birds_can_sleep_while_flying_usin": "Wasu tsuntsaye za su iya barci yayin tashi, suna amfani da “barcin rabin kwakwalwa” — suna rufe rabi ɗaya na kwakwalwa a lokaci guda. An rubuta Frigatebirds suna barci minti 42 a rana a lokacin tashe-tashe na kwana 10 na ƙetare teku, suna ɗaukar ƙananan barci na daƙiƙa 12 kowanne.",
      "navigation_clock": "Agogon Kewayawa",
      "birds_maintain_an_internal_circadian_c": "Tsuntsaye suna kula da agogon circadian na ciki mai matuƙar daidaito. Wannan agogo yana rama motsin rana a sararin sama (kamfas na rana da aka rama lokaci) kuma yana bin canje-canjen yanayi na tsawon rana da ke haddasa hormones na ƙaura.",
      "zugunruhe": "Zugunruhe",
      "zugunruhe_migration_restlessness_is_a_": "Zugunruhe (“rashin nutsuwa na ƙaura”) yanayi ne na hali inda tsuntsaye masu ƙaura da aka tsare a keji ke buga fikafikai zuwa alkiblar da za su yi ƙaura ta halitta, a lokacin da za su yi ƙaura. Ana haddasa shi da hormones kuma an tsara shi ta gado. Ko tsuntsayen da aka tashe da hannu waɗanda ba su da kwarewar ƙaura suna nuna Zugunruhe.",
      "species_comparison": "📊 Kwatancin Nau'i",
      "canada_goose": "Canada Goose",
      "3_000_ft": "ƙafa 3,000",
      "arctic_tern": "Arctic Tern",
