      "available_energy_18_kcal": "Kuzarin da ake da shi: ~18 kcal",
      "flight_metabolic_rate_0_8_kcal_hr": "Yawan metabolism na tashi: ~0.8 kcal/sa'a",
      "crossing_time_20_hours_at_25_mph": "Lokacin ƙetare: ~sa'o'i 20 a 25 mph",
      "energy_required_16_kcal": "Kuzarin da ake buƙata: ~16 kcal",
      "margin_of_safety_2_kcal_11": "Iyakar aminci: ~2 kcal (11%)",
      "that_is_an_incredibly_thin_margin_a_st": "Wannan iyaka ce mai siriri ƙwarai. Iska mai ƙarfi ta gaba, fuskar sanyi, ko isa gaɓar teku da ƙarancin nauyi na 10% zai iya zama mutuwa. Shi ya sa ingancin mazaunin wurin tsayawa yana da ",
      "literally_life_or_death": "batun rai ko mutuwa a zahiri",
      "for_migratory_birds": " ga tsuntsaye masu ƙaura.",
      "push_through_the_weather": "Tura ta cikin yanayi",
      "find_shelter_and_wait": "Nemi mafaka ka jira",
      "detour_around": "Zaga kewaye",
      "keep_flying": "Ci gaba da tashi",
      "land_and_rest": "Sauka ka huta",
      "ride_thermals": "Hau magudanan zafi",
      "animated_night_sky_showing_nocturnal_b": "Sararin daren mai motsi yana nuna ƙaura na tsuntsaye da dare. Taurari suna haske kewaye da Tauraron Arewa, layukan filin maganadisu suna lanƙwasa a sararin sama, kuma ƙaramin garke yana ƙaura ta cikin yanayin. Yana nuna yadda tsuntsaye ke amfani da taurari da jin maganadisu don kewayawa da dare.",
      "how_birds_navigate": "🧭 Yadda Tsuntsaye ke Kewayawa",
