      "migration_complete": "Ƙaura ta Kammala!",
      "migration_failed": "Ƙaura ta Gaza",
      "try_the_migration_challenge_again": "Sake gwada ƙalubalen ƙaura",
      "try_again": "🔄 Sake Gwadawa",
      "threats_to_migratory_birds": "⚠️ Barazana ga Tsuntsaye Masu Ƙaura",
      "migratory_birds_face_growing_dangers_u": "Tsuntsaye masu ƙaura suna fuskantar haɗari masu ƙaruwa. Fahimtar waɗannan barazana shine matakin farko zuwa kiyayewa.",
      "what_you_can_do": "🌱 Abin da Za Ka Iya Yi",
      "lights_out": "Kashe Fitilu: ",
      "turn_off_unnecessary_lights_during_spr": "Kashe fitilun da ba dole ba a lokacin ƙaura na bazara da kaka (Maris-Mayu, Agusta-Nuwamba). Ko da gini ɗaya mai duhu zai iya ceton ɗaruruwan tsuntsaye a dare.",
      "window_decals": "Alamun Taga: ",
      "apply_bird_safe_decals_to_windows_bird": "Sanya alamun aminci ga tsuntsaye a tagogi. Tsuntsaye suna ganin hoton sararin sama da bishiyoyi a gilashi, ba gilashin kansa ba. Alamun da aka sanya a tazarar cm 5 suna karya hotuna.",
      "native_plants": "Tsire-tsiren Gida: ",
      "plant_native_trees_and_shrubs_that_pro": "Dasa bishiyoyi da ciyayi na gida da ke samar da 'ya'yan itace da jawo ƙwari — muhimmin mai ga tsuntsaye masu ƙaura. Tsire-tsiren da ba na gida ba galibi ba su da ƙwari da tsuntsaye ke buƙata.",
      "keep_cats_inside": "Ajiye Kuliyoyi a Ciki: ",
      "indoor_cats_live_longer_healthier_live": "Kuliyoyin ciki suna rayuwa tsawon lokaci, mafi lafiya kuma suna ceton tsuntsaye. Kowa ya ci nasara.",
      "citizen_science": "Kimiyyar Jama'a: ",
      "use_apps_like_ebird_cornell_lab_to_rep": "Yi amfani da manhajoji kamar eBird (Cornell Lab) don ba da rahoton lura da tsuntsaye. Bayananka suna taimaka wa masana kimiyya su bi lokacin ƙaura da yanayin yawan jama'a.",
      "support_habitat": "Tallafa wa Mazauni: ",
      "advocate_for_wetland_protection_and_re": "Ba da shawara don kare fadama da sanya makamashin iska cikin hankali a cikin al'ummarka.",
      "did_you_know": "🤔 Ko Ka Sani?",
      "on_peak_migration_nights": "A daren mafi girman ƙaura ",
      "over_500_million_birds": "tsuntsaye sama da miliyan 500",
      "are_in_the_air_over_north_america_simu": " suna cikin iska a kan Arewacin Amurka a lokaci guda. Tashoshin radar na yanayi suna gano manyan gizagizai na tsuntsaye masu ƙaura suna tashi da faɗuwar rana. Za ka iya kallon ƙaura a lokaci na gaske a BirdCast (birdcast.info).",
      "most_songbird_migration_happens_at_nig": "Yawancin ƙaura na tsuntsayen waƙa yana faruwa da dare, sa'ad da iska ta natsu, masu farauta kaɗan ne, kuma taurari suna bayyana don kewayawa. Tsuntsaye suna amfani da ",
      "setting_sun": "faɗuwar rana",
      "to_calibrate_their_star_compass_at_dus": " don daidaita kamfas ɗin taurarinsu da yamma.",
      "magnetic_sense": "Jin maganadisu",
      "of_birds_may_work_through_quantum_mech": " na tsuntsaye zai iya aiki ta hanyar makanikan ƙididdiga (quantum). Sunadaran cryptochrome a idon tsuntsaye za su iya amfani da haɗakar ƙididdiga don gano filin maganadisu na Duniya — suna sa kewayawar tsuntsu ta zama ɗaya daga cikin ƙananan hanyoyin nazarin halittu da suka dogara da kimiyyar lissafi ta ƙididdiga.",
      "some_bird_species_can_detect_the": "Wasu nau'ikan tsuntsaye za su iya gano ",
      "polarization_pattern": "tsarin polarization",
      "of_sunlight_even_through_heavy_cloud_c": " na hasken rana ko da ta cikin gizagizai masu kauri, ta amfani da cones na musamman masu jin UV a retina ɗinsu. Wannan yana nufin ko da a ranakun gizagizai tsuntsaye za su iya tantance matsayin rana kuma su kula da hanyarsu.",
      "the_brain_s_memory_center_is_significa": " (cibiyar ƙwaƙwalwar kwakwalwa) ya fi girma sosai a nau'ikan tsuntsaye masu ƙaura fiye da nau'ikan da ba sa ƙaura. A zahiri yana girma a lokacin ƙaura, yana ƙara neurons sabbi a wani tsari da ake kira neurogenesis na manya. Yana sake ƙanƙanta bayan ƙaura. Wannan sassaucin yanayi na kwakwalwa fanni ne mai muhimmanci na kimiyyar jijiyoyi.",
      "migration_vocabulary": "📖 Kalmomin Ƙaura",
