      "pre_industrial_1750": "Kafin masana'antu (1750)",
      "stable_for_10_000_years_holocene_clima": "Ya tabbata shekaru 10,000. Yanayin Holocene da dukan wayewar ɗan adam ya girma a ciki.",
      "keeling_starts_measuring_1958": "Keeling ya fara aunawa (1958)",
      "charles_david_keeling_begins_continuou": "Charles David Keeling ya fara sa ido kai tsaye kan CO₂ a Mauna Loa. Lanƙwasarsa ta tabbatar da cewa ɗumamar da ɗan adam ya jawo gaskiya ce.",
      "350_ppm_1988": "350 ppm (1988)",
      "climate_scientist_james_hansen_tells_u": "Masanin yanayi James Hansen ya gaya wa Majalisar Amurka cewa ɗumama ta fara. 350.org tana ganin 350 ppm a matsayin iyaka “mai aminci”.",
      "400_ppm_2013": "400 ppm (2013)",
      "first_time_atmospheric_co_crossed_400_": "Karo na farko da CO₂ na sararin samaniya ya wuce 400 ppm cikin shekaru miliyan 3+. Zamanin ƙarshe na 400 ppm na Duniya: dazuzzukan tropics a sandunan duniya.",
      "420_ppm_2023": "420 ppm (2023)",
      "current_level_highest_in_at_least_800_": "Matakin yanzu. Mafi girma cikin aƙalla shekaru 800,000 (daga cores na kankara). Daidai da ~1.2°C na ɗumama.",
      "450_ppm_projected_2035": "450 ppm (an ƙiyasta ~2035)",
      "threshold_associated_with_2_c_warming_": "Iyaka mai alaƙa da ɗumamar 2°C idan ta dawwama. Manufar Yarjejeniyar Paris: kasancewa ƙasa da 1.5°C.",
      "tropical_coral_reef_die_off": "Mutuwar Murjani na Tropics",
      "mass_coral_bleaching_events_hit_the_gr": "Manyan al'amuran fararen murjani sun buga Great Barrier Reef a 2016, 2017, 2020, 2022, da 2024. A ɗumamar 1.5°C, 70–90% na murjanin tropics suna mutuwa. A 2°C, 99% suna mutuwa.",
      "greenland_ice_sheet_collapse": "Rushewar Kankara na Greenland",
      "the_greenland_ice_sheet_holds_enough_w": "Kankara na Greenland yana da isasshen ruwa don ɗaga matakin teku mita 7 (23 ft). A ~1.5°C mai dawwama, narkewa ta zama wadda ba za a iya juyawa ba cikin ƙarnuka zuwa dubban shekaru.",
      "amoc_collapse_gulf_stream": "Rushewar AMOC (Gulf Stream)",
      "the_atlantic_meridional_overturning_ci": "Zagayen AMOC yana ɗaukar zafi daga tropics zuwa Turai. Ya raunana 15% tun 1950. Cikakken tsayawa zai sanyaya arewacin Turai sosai yayin da yake ɓata damina a Afirka da Asiya.",
      "amazon_rainforest_dieback": "Koma-bayan Dajin Ruwan Amazon",
      "the_amazon_generates_half_its_own_rain": "Amazon yana samar da rabin ruwan samansa da kansa. Da sare bishiyoyi na 20–25% + hauhawar zafi, yana cikin haɗarin juyawa daga dajin ruwa zuwa savanna. Wasu binciken suna nuni cewa iyakar tana kusa da 2°C a saurin sare na yanzu.",
      "permafrost_methane_release": "Sakin Methane na Permafrost",
      "arctic_permafrost_holds_twice_the_carb": "Permafrost na Arctic yana da carbon ninki biyu na wanda ke sararin samaniya yanzu. Da ɗumama 3–4× da sauri fiye da matsakaicin duniya, ya riga yana narkewa yana sakin CO₂ da methane (mai ƙarfi 28× fiye da CO₂ cikin shekaru 100).",
      "west_antarctic_ice_sheet": "Kankara na Yammacin Antarctica",
      "marine_based_ice_sheets_anchored_below": "Kankara na teku da ke ƙarƙashin matakin teku. Ruwan teku mai zafi yana zaizayar da su daga ƙasa. Kankarar Thwaites (“Doomsday Glacier”) shi ne babban haɗari. Rushewa zai ɗaga matakin teku mita 3.3 (11 ft).",
      "boreal_forest_die_off": "Mutuwar Dajin Boreal",
      "northern_coniferous_forests_russia_can": "Dazuzzukan arewa masu allura (Rasha, Kanada, Scandinavia) suna cikin damuwa daga ɗumama, ƙwarin haushi, da gobarar daji. Cikakken sauyawa zuwa ciyayi zai iya sakin carbon mai yawa da aka adana.",
      "gulf_of_maine_rapid_warming": "Ɗumamar Sauri na Gulf of Maine",
      "the_gulf_of_maine_has_warmed_faster_th": "Gulf of Maine ya ɗumama da sauri fiye da 99% na tekunan duniya tun 1980 — kusan 0.5°F kowane shekaru goma, kimanin 3× na matsakaicin teku na duniya. Igiyar sanyi ta Labrador ta raunana yayin da ruwan zafi na Gulf Stream ke kaiwa arewa sosai, yana sake tsara sarƙar abinci a lokaci na ainihi tun daga tushe. Al'ummomin bakin teku na Penobscot, Passamaquoddy, Maliseet, da Mi’kmaq sun rubuta waɗannan canje-canje a rubutun baki shekaru da dama kafin tauraron ɗan adam ya tabbatar.",
      "onshore_wind_turbines": "Injinan Iska na Kan Ƙasa",
      "cheapest_electricity_worldwide_in_2024": "Wutar lantarki mafi arha a duniya a 2024. Iyawa tana ninkawa kowace shekara a yankuna da yawa.",
      "utility_scale_solar_farms": "Gonakin Rana na Matakin Kayan Aiki",
      "cheapest_electricity_in_history_grid_i": "Wutar lantarki mafi arha a tarihi. Haɗa grid shi ne babban ƙalubale yanzu.",
      "rooftop_solar": "Rana na Rufin Gida",
      "distributed_resilient_typical_5kw_syst": "Wadda aka rarraba + mai juriya. Dawowar kuɗi na tsarin 5kW na yau da kullun: shekaru 6–10.",
      "reduced_food_waste": "Rage Ɓarnar Abinci",
      "1_3_of_food_is_wasted_preventing_waste": "1/3 na abinci ana ɓata. Hana ɓarna yana guje wa methane daga juji KUMA fitarwar noman abinci.",
      "plant_rich_diets": "Cin Abinci Mai Yawan Tsirrai",
      "not_100_vegan_even_cutting_beef_3_a_we": "Ba 100% vegan ba — har rage naman shanu 3× a mako yana da tasiri mai girma. Yana 'yantar da ƙasa don sake dashen daji.",
      "tropical_forest_restoration": "Maido da Dajin Tropics",
      "restore_125m_hectares_protects_biodive": "Maido da hekta 125M. Yana kare bambancin halittu + yana janyo CO₂ ta hanyar photosynthesis.",
      "temperate_forest_restoration": "Maido da Dajin Yanayi Mai Sanyi",
      "plant_where_natural_conditions_support": "Dasa inda yanayin halitta ke tallafa wa girma. Ƙarin fa'idodi: sanyaya, kare wuraren ruwa.",
      "silvopasture": "Kiwo na Daji",
      "integrating_trees_into_grazing_land_li": "Haɗa bishiyoyi cikin ƙasar kiwo. Dabbobi suna samun inuwa; ƙasa tana adana carbon 4× fiye da ƙasar kiwo mara komai.",
      "regenerative_agriculture": "Noma Mai Sabuntawa",
      "no_till_cover_crops_diverse_rotations_": "Ba noma ba + amfanin gona na rufi + jujjuya iri-iri. Yana gina carbon na ƙasa yayin da yake kiyaye amfani.",
      "peatlands_protection": "Kare Ƙasar Peat",
      "peatlands_store_3_more_carbon_than_for": "Ƙasar peat tana adana carbon 3× fiye da dazuzzuka a duniya. Peat da aka busar = babban mai fitarwa.",
      "refrigerant_management": "Sarrafa Kayan Sanyaya",
      "hfcs_are_1_000_9_000_more_potent_than_": "Iskar HFCs tana da ƙarfi 1,000–9,000× fiye da CO₂. Gyaran Kigali (2016) yana cire su a hankali.",
      "electric_vehicles_personal": "Motocin Lantarki (na kai)",
      "evs_produce_50_70_less_lifetime_emissi": "EV suna samar da fitarwar rayuwa 50–70% ƙasa fiye da man fetur — yana inganta yayin da grid ke tsafta.",
      "public_transit_rail": "Sufurin Jama'a + Jirgin Ƙasa",
      "electric_trains_move_a_passenger_km_at": "Jiragen ƙasa na lantarki suna motsa fasinja-km da 1/10 na fitarwar mota.",
      "bike_infrastructure": "Ababen Keke",
      "dutch_cycling_cities_have_1_3_the_tran": "Biranen keke na Holland suna da 1/3 na fitarwar sufuri. Ababen more rayuwa suna ƙirƙirar ɗabi'a.",
      "building_retrofits": "Gyaran Gine-gine",
      "insulation_heat_pumps_led_lighting_us_": "Insulation + fanfunan zafi + fitilun LED. Gine-ginen Amurka suna amfani da 40% na makamashin farko.",
      "heat_pumps": "Fanfunan Zafi",
      "3_4_more_efficient_than_gas_furnaces_w": "Mai inganci 3–4× fiye da tandurun gas. Suna aiki har zuwa −15°C a samfuran yanayi mai sanyi na zamani.",
      "girls_education_family_planning": "Ilimin 'Yan Mata da Tsara Iyali",
      "consistently_top_ranked_educated_women": "Koyaushe a saman jerin. Mata masu ilimi suna da 'ya'ya kaɗan KUMA rayuwa mai tasiri sosai. Yana taruwa a tsararraki.",
      "clean_cookstoves": "Murhun Girki Masu Tsafta",
      "replaces_wood_charcoal_fires_benefits_": "Yana maye gurbin wutar itace/gawayi. Fa'idodi: yanayi + gurɓataccen iska na cikin gida (yana kashe 4M/shekara) + sare dazuzzuka.",
