      "average_us_household_emits_16_tons_co_": "Gida na matsakaici na Amurka yana fitar da ~ton 16 na CO₂/shekara. Manyan na'urori su ne dumama gida, sufuri, da cin abinci — ba bambaron robobi ba.",
      "renewable_energy": "Makamashi mai sabuntawa",
      "solar_wind_are_now_cheaper_than_new_fo": "Rana + iska yanzu sun fi arha fiye da sabbin masana'antun burbushin mai a yawancin kasuwanni. Sashen mai wuya shi ne haɗa grid, ba tsadar samarwa ba.",
      "the_keeling_curve": "Lanƙwasar Keeling",
      "continuous_co_measurement_at_mauna_loa": "Auna CO₂ kai tsaye a Mauna Loa tun 1958 — rikodin sararin samaniya mafi tsawon aiki. Tsarin haƙoran zare ya samo asali ne daga photosynthesis na Arewacin Duniya.",
      "climate_tipping_points": "Wuraren juyawa na yanayi",
      "thresholds_where_the_system_shifts_sta": "Iyakoki inda tsarin ke canza yanayi ya kuma tsaya a can — narkewar Greenland, koma-bayan Amazon, raguwar AMOC. Aiki na baya-bayan nan yana nuni cewa da yawa na iya kusa fiye da yadda aka zata.",
      "climate_justice_2": "Adalcin yanayi",
      "the_countries_that_emitted_the_least_f": "Ƙasashen da suka fitar mafi ƙanƙanta suna fuskantar mafi munin tasiri. Yanayi batu ne na adalci da farko — rauni yana bin kuɗin shiga, yanki, da alhaki na tarihi.",
      "solutions_toolkit": "Kayan Aikin Mafita",
      "drawdown_ranks_100_solutions_by_gigato": "Drawdown yana jera mafita 100 bisa gigatons na CO₂ da aka guje. Kayan sanyaya, ɓarnar abinci, da ilmantar da 'yan mata suna kan gaba — ba abin da yawancin mutane ke tsammani ba.",
