      "baseline_today_s_coastlines": "Tushe — bakin tekun yau.",
      "locked_in_at_1_5_c_sustained_warming_m": "An kulle a ~1.5°C na ɗumama mai dawwama. Yawancin daidaita bakin teku har yanzu yana yiwuwa da katangar teku, ja da baya da aka sarrafa.",
      "associated_with_2_5_c_warming_displace": "Mai alaƙa da ~2.5°C na ɗumama. Yana raba mutane fiye da kowane yaƙi a tarihi. Ambaliyar guguwa ta zama masifa ga yankunan cikin gida.",
      "likely_by_2300_at_3_c_entire_nations_l": "Mai yiwuwa nan da 2300 a 3°C. Ƙasashe gaba ɗaya suna rasa yankin da za a iya zama. New Orleans, Venice, da yawancin Vietnam.",
      "multi_century_commitment_at_4_c_warmin": "Alkawari na ƙarnuka da yawa a ɗumamar 4°C. Yana buƙatar rushewar Greenland + Yammacin Antarctica. Ana sake rubuta yanayin bakin teku na wayewar ɗan adam har abada.",
