      "no_major_political_or_climate_event_ro": "Babu wani babban al'amari na siyasa ko yanayi. Aikin manufa na yau da kullun ya ci gaba.",
      "net_zero_plus_equity": "Sifili Cikakke da Adalci",
      "you_hit_deep_decarbonization_across_se": "Ka cimma cire carbon mai zurfi a fannoni, ka gina juriya, ka kuma sanya adalci a tsakiya. Haka nasarar sauyin yanayi take yayin da yarjejeniyar zamantakewa ta riƙe.",
      "decarbonized_but_uneven": "An Cire Carbon amma Ba Daidai ba",
      "significant_decarbonization_across_the": "Cire carbon mai yawa a fannonin makamashi da sufuri, amma daidaitawa da adalci sun ragu baya. Lanƙwasoshin carbon daidai ne; haɗin gwiwar siyasa mai rauni ne.",
      "partial_progress": "Ci Gaba na Ɓangare",
      "some_sectors_moved_others_stalled_publ": "Wasu fannonin sun ci gaba. Wasu sun tsaya cak. Goyon bayan jama'a ya lalace da lokaci. Wannan ita ce hanyar da yawancin manufofin yanayi na duniya na gaske suka bi.",
      "climate_policy_failure": "Gazawar Manufar Yanayi",
      "decarbonization_stalled_adaptation_gap": "Cire carbon ya tsaya cak. Gibin daidaitawa ya faɗaɗa. Goyon bayan jama'a ya rushe. Wannan ita ce hanyar da muke ƙoƙarin gujewa: tasirin yanayi na taruwa ba tare da ababen zamantakewa ko fasaha na amsawa ba.",
      "initial_conditions_are_workable_spread": "Yanayin farko yana yiwuwa. Rarraba jari a fannoni 2-3 a lokaci na farko don gano waɗanne dokokin amsawa ke fara aiki. Ilimin jama'a + majalisun 'yan ƙasa suna biya a hankali amma da dawwama.",
