      "medical_diagnosis_legal_advice_citing_": "Ganewar cuta, shawarar shari'a, nassin tushen farko da ba za ka iya tabbatarwa ba — kayan aiki mara kyau ga aikin. Yi amfani da ƙwararren ɗan adam ko tushe mai iko.",
      "trust_calibration_how_much_should_i_tr": "🔬 Daidaita amincewa — nawa ne ya kamata in amince da wannan sakamako?",
      "set_task_familiarity_stakes_source_qua": "Saita sabawa da aiki, haɗari, ingancin tushe, da amincewar da samfurin ya bayyana. Ƙididdiga inda kewayon amincewa ke faɗuwa. Babu maki, babu bayyanawa.",
