      "build_the_double_helix_from_4_letters": "Gina double helix daga haruffa 4",
      "a_pairs_with_t_2_bonds_g_with_c_3_wats": "A yana haɗuwa da T (bond 2), G da C (3). Watson + Crick + Franklin (1953) sun warware wannan siffa daga X-ray crystallography. Wannan siffar tana nuna yadda DNA ke kwafan kansa da yadda ake karanta shi.",
