      "helicase_splits_the_strands_dna_polyme": "Helicase yana raba strand; DNA polymerase yana gina strand na cikawa. Semi-conservative — kowane sabon helix yana da strand ɗaya na tsoho + ɗaya sabo. Meselson da Stahl sun tabbatar da wannan a 1958.",
      "transcribe_dna_mrna_in_the_nucleus": "Transcribe — DNA → mRNA (a cikin nucleus)",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_one_dna_strand_3_": "RNA polymerase yana karanta DNA strand ɗaya 3′→5′ kuma yana gina RNA 5′→3′. Haruffa iri ɗaya ne, sai dai T ya zama U. mRNA yana ɗaukar girke-girke zuwa ribosome — matakin farko na central dogma.",
      "translate_mrna_protein_at_the_ribosome": "Fassara — mRNA → protein (a ribosome)",
      "64_codons_20_amino_acids_the_genetic_c": "codon 64 → amino acid 20 (genetic code yana da yawa). AUG yana farawa; UAA/UAG/UGA suna dakatarwa. tRNA yana karanta codon, yana kawo amino acid daidai, yana gina peptide bond.",
      "mutate_substitution_insertion_deletion": "Mutate — maye gurbi, sakawa, gogewa",
      "point_mutation_one_letter_swapped_inse": "Point mutation — an canza harafi ɗaya. Insertion/deletion — reading frame yana motsi, dukan protein na ƙasa yana lalacewa. Sickle cell anemia A→T ɗaya ne kawai — harafi ɗaya, tasiri na rayuwa duka.",
      "crispr_the_precision_edit": "CRISPR — gyara madaidaici",
      "bacterial_immune_system_repurposed_cas": "An sake amfani da tsarin garkuwa na ƙwayoyin cuta. Cas9 enzyme + guide RNA = almakashi na molecule. Doudna + Charpentier sun lashe Nobel 2020. CRISPR therapy na farko (sickle cell) FDA ya amince da shi a Disamba 2023.",
      "protein_fold_function_malfunction": "Protein — naɗewa, aiki, lahani",
      "sequence_determines_structure_determin": "Sequence yana ƙayyade tsari wanda yake ƙayyade aiki. Hemoglobin yana ɗaukar O₂, antibody suna ganewa, enzyme suna catalyze. AlphaFold (2020) ya yi hasashen tsari miliyan 200 — matsala mai shekaru 50 an warware a cikin watanni 18.",
      "forensics_str_profiling_dna_evidence": "Kimiyyar shari'a — STR profiling + shaidar DNA",
      "codis_uses_20_short_tandem_repeat_str_": "CODIS yana amfani da short tandem repeat (STR) loci 20. Yiwuwar dacewa ɗaya ce cikin quadrillion lokacin da dukan loci suka dace. Innocence Project — an soke hukunce-hukunce sama da 245 na kuskure ta hanyar gwajin DNA bayan laifi.",
      "challenge_graded_problems": "Ƙalubale — matsaloli masu maki",
      "practice_transcription_translation_mut": "Yi motsa jiki na transcription, translation, rarraba mutation. AP Bio Big Idea 3.A.1 — DNA (wani lokaci RNA) shine tushen watsa bayanan gado. NGSS HS-LS3-1.",
      "battle_head_to_head_retrieval": "Yaƙi — dawowa fuska da fuska",
      "retrieval_practice_gamified_speed_buil": "Motsa jiki na dawowa — a matsayin wasa. Gudu yana gina automaticity — lokacin da duban codon table ya zama na atomatik, working memory naka yana samun 'yanci don tunani mafi girma, kamar hasashen tasirin mutation.",
      "learn_the_central_dogma_history": "Koya — central dogma + tarihi",
      "dna_rna_protein_with_retroviruses_hiv_": "DNA → RNA → protein — ciki har da retrovirus (HIV) da ke tafiya baya ta hanyar reverse transcriptase. Crick ya ƙirƙiri kalmar \"dogma\" a 1957; daga baya ya ce yana nufin zato, ba gaskiya da ba za a iya musantawa ba.",
      "build_a_dna_strand": "Gina DNA strand",
      "pick_a_sequence_the_complementary_stra": "Zaɓi sequence — ana cika strand na cikawa da base pairing (A-T, G-C). DNA na gaskiya ana gina shi haka koyaushe.",
      "dna_replication": "DNA replication",
      "helicase_unwinds_the_helix_dna_polymer": "Helicase yana buɗe helix; DNA polymerase yana karanta kowane template strand kuma yana sanya cikawarsa. Semi-conservative — kowane daughter strand yana da ɗaya na tsoho + ɗaya sabo.",
      "transcription_dna_mrna": "Transcription — DNA → mRNA",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_the_template_stra": "RNA polymerase yana karanta template strand. Ka'ida iri ɗaya ta complementarity, amma T → U. Sakamako — kwafi ɗaya na mRNA na single-strand, a shirye don fita daga nucleus.",
      "translation_mrna_protein": "Translation — mRNA → protein",
      "ribosome_reads_codons_3_bases_at_a_tim": "Ribosome yana karanta codon (base 3 kowane lokaci). Kowane codon → amino acid ɗaya. Ana karanta genetic code a matsayin triplet mara jujjuyawa, mara waƙafi.",
      "mutations": "Mutations",
