      "gut_microbes_communicate_with_brain_vi": "Gut microbe suna sadarwa da kwakwalwa ta vagus nerve, immune signal, metabolite. An haɗa da mood, hali — amma da'awa da yawa na musamman an wuce gona da iri.",
