      "fecal_microbiota_transplant_fmt_cures_": "Fecal microbiota transplant (FMT) yana warkar da recurrent C. difficile infection a ~90% na lokuta. Sauran aikace-aikace har yanzu experimental.",
      "varies_by_body_site_forehead_oily_domi": "Yana bambanta ta body site — goshi (mai mai, Cutibacterium acnes yana mulki), hanji (anaerobe), hamata (gumin apocrine + bacteria → ƙamshin jiki).",
