      "reactivate_telomerase_telomeres_mainta": "Reactivate telomerase → ana kula da telomere → rabuwa mara iyaka.",
      "tumors_recruit_blood_vessels_to_feed_g": "Tumor suna ɗaukar tasoshin jini don ciyar da mass mai girma.",
      "cells_lose_adhesion_migrate_colonize_d": "cell suna rasa adhesion, suna ƙaura, suna mallaka tissue masu nisa.",
      "warburg_effect_tumors_use_glycolysis_e": "Warburg effect — tumor suna amfani da glycolysis ko da akwai oxygen.",
