      "chronic_inflammation_creates_a_permiss": "Ciwon kumburi na dindindin yana ƙirƙirar muhalli mai bada dama.",
      "accumulating_mutations_chromosomal_rea": "mutation masu taruwa + chromosomal rearrangement suna tafiyar da evolution.",
      "fast_non_specific_skin_mucus_complemen": "Da sauri, non-specific. Fata, mucus, complement, neutrophil, NK cell, macrophage.",
