      "y_shaped_proteins_5_classes_igg_most_a": "Protein masu siffar Y. class 5 — IgG (mafi yawa), IgA (mucosa), IgM (na farko), IgE (rashin lafiyar jiki + parasite), IgD (B-cell surface).",
      "cell_surface_molecules_that_present_an": "cell surface molecule da ke gabatar da antigen ga T cell. MHC I (dukan cell, viral peptide). MHC II (immune cell, extracellular peptide).",
