      "most_untrained_voices_span_1_5_2_octav": "Yawancin muryoyin da ba a horar da su ba suna faɗaɗa octave 1.5-2; mawaƙa na gargajiya masu horo suna kaiwa 3 ko fiye. Faɗaɗa yanki galibi game da haɗa rejista ne, ba kawai miƙawa sama da ƙasa ba.",
      "vibrato_lab_2": "Dakin Gwaje-gwaje na Vibrato",
      "healthy_vibrato_5_7_hz_oscillation_60_": "Vibrato mai ƙoshin lafiya: girgiza 5-7 Hz, da faɗin ~60-100 cents. A hankali = girgiza; da sauri = rawa. Vibrato sakamakon tallafin numfashi mai kwanciya ne, ba dabara ta daban ba.",
      "interval_singer_ear_training": "Mai Waƙar Tazara — Horar da Kunne",
      "major_3rd_vs_minor_3rd_is_the_single_m": "Na uku babba da na uku ƙarama shine mafi rikitarwa nau'i-biyu na tazara ga masu farawa. Alamun tunawa: na uku babba = \"Oh when the saints\", na uku ƙarama = \"Greensleeves\". Yana gina jin gaɓɓai.",
      "lip_trills_sirens_before_any_sustained": "Girgizar leɓe + ƙara kafin kowace waƙa mai tsayi. Mintuna 5-10 na dumama mai ƙarancin ƙarfi yana rage haɗarin yawan amfani da igiyoyin murya da rabi. Tsallake dumama shine dalili na 1 na raunukan murya da za a iya hanawa.",
      "sight_reading_2": "Karanta Rubutu",
      "solf_ge_do_re_mi_letter_names_for_sigh": "Solfège (do-re-mi) ya fi sunayen haruffa kyau don karanta rubutu saboda gaɓoɓi suna ɓoye alaƙar tazara, ba kawai lambobin tsayin murya ba. Do mai motsi ya fi do tsayayye kyau don kiɗan toni.",
      "resonance_lab_discover_your_vocal_tone": "Dakin Gwaje-gwaje na Amsawa — Gano Launin Muryarka",
      "two_sliders_throat_openness_and_soft_p": "Zame biyu — buɗewar maƙogwaro da ɗaga rufin baki mai laushi — suna haɗuwa zuwa halaye huɗu na launin murya (mai wadata, mai haske, mai ɗumi, na hanci). Babu maki, babu bayyanawa: gwada, rubuta, kuma ka bayyana abin da ka gano.",
      "rich_open_lifted": "🎶 Mai wadata (a buɗe + a ɗaga)",
      "operatic_professional_tone_full_resona": "Launin murya na opera / ƙwararru. Cikakkiyar amsawa.",
      "bright_open_lowered": "✨ Mai haske (a buɗe + a saukar)",
      "forward_placement_pop_belt_style": "Sanya gaba. Salon pop / belting.",
      "warm_narrow_lifted": "🌅 Mai ɗumi (mai ƙunci + a ɗaga)",
      "mellow_tone_choral_acoustic": "Launin murya mai laushi. Mawaƙa / akustik.",
      "nasal_narrow_lowered": "🐝 Na hanci (mai ƙunci + a saukar)",
      "tight_resonance_often_unintended": "Amsawa mai tsauri. Galibi ba da gangan ba.",
      "resonance_discovery": "🎙️ Gano Amsawa",
      "sliders_for_throat_openness_soft_palat": "Zame don buɗewar maƙogwaro, ɗaga rufin baki mai laushi. Rarrabuwa daban da launukan murya 4. Babu maki, babu bayyanawa.",
      "hypothesis_what_anatomical_adjustments": "Zato: Wane gyare-gyaren jiki ne ke haifar da launin murya mai wadata?",
      "why_do_classical_singers_lift_the_pala": "Me yasa mawaƙan gargajiya ke ɗaga rufin baki?",
      "how_does_throat_openness_affect_overto": "Yaya buɗewar maƙogwaro ke shafar jerin sautunan sama?",
      "explain_how_resonance_cavity_shape_con": "Bayyana yadda sifar ramin amsawa ke sarrafa launin murya.",
      "design_note_discrete_4_tone_marker_no_": "Bayanin ƙira: alamar launin murya 4 daban; babu makin akustik; babu bayyanawa — da gangan."
