      "blur_amount_hint": "(2px ≈ ɗan rauni a gani; 5-8px ≈ mai tsanani)",
      "blur_amount_aria": "Blur amount pixels",
      "stop": "Tsayar simulator",
      "motor_toast": "Motor impairment simulation: gani info kati.",
      "tip": "shawara: gwada launi-blindness simulators kan darasi wancan yana amfani red/green zuwa convey meaning (correct/incorrect, gargadi/safe). idan meaning shi ne lost simulation, original design shi ne failing ɗalibi tare da wancan condition. Ƙara alama, labels, ko patterns alongside launi.",
      "items": {
        "blur_label": "Ɓarna ta rauni a gani",
        "blur_desc": "Approximates uncorrected low vision (gani acuity worse than 20/40). Roughly 4% na population has uncorrected refractive kuskure ko other low-vision conditions; wannan raba shi ne much higher among older adults da ɗalibi tare da gani impairments.",
        "protanopia_label": "Protanopia (rashin ganin ja)",
        "protanopia_desc": "Severe red-green launi vision deficiency, missing L-cone. About 1% na males da very rare females. Reds appear darker; reds da greens su ne confused.",
        "deuteranopia_label": "Deuteranopia (rashin ganin kore)",
        "deuteranopia_desc": "most common form na launi blindness, missing M-cone. About 6% na males. Reds da greens appear similar; most common form na red-green launi vision deficiency.",
        "tritanopia_label": "Tritanopia (rashin ganin shuɗi)",
        "tritanopia_desc": "Rare form, missing S-cone. About 0.01% na population. Blues appear greenish; yellow-blue distinctions su ne lost.",
        "achromatopsia_label": "Achromatopsia (no launi)",
        "achromatopsia_desc": "Kammala absence na launi vision. Affects roughly 0.003% na population (about 1 30,000). world appears shades na grey.",
        "dyslexia_label": "Dyslexia gani stress",
        "dyslexia_desc": "LIMITED kwaikwayo na one common gani-stress gogewa some dyslexic readers report (slight blur, lower contrast, shifting spacing). Dyslexia shi ne highly individual; wannan shi ne one slice, ba definitive rendering. About 5-10% na ɗalibi yana da dyslexia.",
        "motor_label": "Nakasun motsi",
        "motor_desc": "Motor impairments resist gani simulation. most authentic jarrabawa shi ne zuwa yi amfani OS-matakin kayan aiki real ɗalibi yi amfani: Windows Sticky Keys, macOS hankali Keys, dwell-danna software, canza shiga (e.g., iOS Canza Control ko Android Canza Shiga). Gwada completing darasi amfani only one hand, only keyboard, ko only one finger."
      }
